Hi there I'm trying to get the value of a selected dropdown from a form using jquery. I'm trying to set the variable currently using

var state = (_$form_.find('input[name="state"]').val());

This works fine for text field (like email) but isn't capturing the value for a dropdown field like state. The console reads the value as 'undefined'. Happy to post more code but I'm sure I'm not targeting the dropdown correctly. Thanks for the help!
